\c 2
\s1 The wine miracle
\p
\v 1 On the Tuesday\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Or possibly, ‘Three days later’.\f*, there was a wedding in Cana in Galilee, and¦63932 Jesus' mother¦63935 was there.
