\p
\v 8 But they double-checked, “Honoured teacher, the Judeans wanted to execute you, so do you really want to go back there again?”
\p
\v 9 And Jesus answered, “There are twelve hours of light in the day. Anyone who walks during the daytime doesn't stumble because he is seeing the light of this world.
