\p
\v 24 “Yes, I know that he'll come back to life at the resurrection on the last day¦73725,” said Martha.
\p
\v 25 But Jesus continued, “\em I am\em* the resurrection and¦73736 the life¦73738. Anyone who believes that I'm from God, even if they die¦73744 they'll still be living,
