\v 8 \x + \xo 12:8: \xt Deu 15:11.\x*You'll always have poor people with you, but you won't always have me here.”
\s1 The leaders also plan to kill Lazarus
\p
\v 9 When it was discovered that Jesus was there, many Judeans started arriving, not only because of Jesus, but¦74662 also to see¦74668 Lazarus who'd been dead¦74674 and¦74654 Jesus had brought him back to life.
\v 10 But the chief priests¦74681 decided in a meeting that they¦74686 should also have Lazarus¦74685 killed,
