\v 13 \x + \xo 12:13: \xt Psa 118:25-26.\x*took \add long\add* branches¦74725 from palm trees¦74727 and brought them out as they went to meet him. They called out, “Honoured saviour! The one coming¦74745 in the authority of the master has been blessed \add by God\add*. He's the king¦74751 of Israel.”
\p
