\p
\v 34 \x + \xo 12:34: \xt Psa 110:4; Isa 9:7; Eze 37:25; Dan 7:14.\x*So the crowd queried him, “We heard from the scriptures that the messiah will stay until the end of the age so why do you¦75193 say that mankind's child will be lifted up. And who is this ‘mankind's child’?”
\p
