\c 21
\s1 The miracle of the net full of fish
\p
\v 1 After all this, Jesus revealed himself again to his trainees at Lake Galilee. It happened like this:
\v 2 Simon Peter, Thomas nicknamed ‘Twin’, Nathanael from Cana in Galilee, the sons¦81746 of Zebedee, and two¦81759 other trainees had gathered together
