\p
\v 11 So Simon Peter went and dragged the net onto the beach. Amazingly it hadn't torn even though it contained 153 large fish.
\v 12 Then Jesus said, “Now, come and have breakfast.” But none of the trainees dared to ask who he was, because they figured it must be the master.
