\s1 Jesus questions Peter
\p
\v 15 While they were eating, Jesus asked Simon Peter, “Simon, son of John, do you love me more than these?”
\p Peter answered, “Yes, master, you know that I love you.”
\p Jesus responded, “Feed my lambs.”
\v 16 Then he asked again, “Simon, son of John, do you love me?”
