\p
\v 20 \x + \xo 21:20: \xt Jn 13:25.\x*When Peter turned¦82243 around he saw that the intern that Jesus loved was following¦82254 them—the one who had leaned on Jesus' chest¦82263 during the supper and asked who the one was who would turn Jesus over.
