\p
\v 22 But Jesus replied, “If I want him to stay alive until I come back, what business would it¦82303 be of yours? You just stay following¦82309 me.”
\p
\v 23 As a result of that, a rumour went around the others that that one would not die, but Jesus never said that. (He only said, “If I want him to stay alive until I come back, what business would it be of yours?”)
\s1 Statement of fact
\p
